"Statera Medical is a pioneering health and medtech company specializing in orthopedic and medical devices, with a focus on shoulder joint replacement implants.

At the forefront of innovation, Statera Medical develops smart and adjustable implants that are tailored to each patient, aiming to enhance quality of life and reduce complications. Their cutting-edge implants combine surgical and technological advancements to improve patient outcomes significantly.

The adjustable prosthesis, equipped with the Goldilocks system, allows precise management of implant thickness to customize surgery for individual patients. By providing objective measurements of soft tissue tension, surgeons can mitigate risks such as fracture, instability, dislocation, and muscle fatigue.

Additionally, Statera Medical offers connected prosthetics that transmit soft tissue tension data to a connection terminal, enabling real-time monitoring during surgery and postoperative care. With an intuitive interface for enhanced surgical processes, Statera Medical is revolutionizing the field of orthopedic implants."

"Airwallex is a prominent fintech company offering integrated solutions for businesses to streamline cross-border transactions. 

Established in 2015, Airwallex has expanded its global presence with over 400 employees across ten international offices. The company has secured substantial venture capital funding exceeding $200 million, with support from renowned investors such as DST Global, Sequoia Capital, Tencent, and Mastercard. 

Recognized as a fintech unicorn in the APAC region, Airwallex's cutting-edge platform facilitates high-speed, cost-effective international payments and seamless receipt of funds worldwide. 

Named among the top 50 fintech companies globally, Airwallex is dedicated to revolutionizing financial services and fostering international business growth in an interconnected digital economy."

"CAMSENS GmbH is a pioneering company in the fields of Animal Health and Artificial Intelligence, revolutionizing pathogen detection for veterinarians and laboratories.

Utilizing efficient and rapid processing systems, CAMSENS doubles the speed of pathogen detection with its digital, fully automated Multiscan scanner. This innovative technology, enhanced by artificial intelligence for customizable image processing, supports high workloads and throughput.

In Animal Health, CAMSENS specializes in detecting parasite eggs in fecal samples of sheep and cattle, with potential applications for other animals and lab tests. Additionally, businesses can rely on CAMSENS for air quality monitoring, detecting mold spores and airborne contaminants with precision.

CAMSENS aims to streamline pathology testing with affordable solutions, reduce employee workload, and enable high-throughput analysis through fully automated processes, ensuring accurate and timely results for clients."

"Bump by Ownors AI is a cutting-edge company at the forefront of Brand & Retail, Deeptech, Fintech, and Supply Chain industries. 

Utilizing artificial intelligence and analytics, Bump offers a revolutionary platform tailored for creators. By tracking and recovering lost revenue, facilitating micro-financing, and arranging personalized live sessions with industry experts, Bump empowers creators to overcome traditional barriers and access essential resources.

With a focus on mentorship and managed micro-advances, Bump by Ownors AI is reshaping the landscape for creators, providing them with the tools and support needed to thrive in the competitive entertainment industry. Through innovative technology and strategic partnerships, Bump is driving innovation and fostering growth within the creator community."
